p><p><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">Any Pakistani holding valid CNIC can =
open their bank account in their choice of <a href=3D"https://www.sbp.org.p=
k/Finc/AMAscheme.html#5">banks available</a> on Asaan Mobile Account platfo=
