	      =20
	              <p style=3D"text-align: justify"><font color=3D"#000" size=
=3D"+1">
	           A valid CNIC card and an active mobile sim is required to open =
a bank account on AMA platform.  </font></p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
	=09
	=09
	    <div class=3D"card">
