se" aria-controls=3D"collapse3"><p class=3D"mbr-text mb-3 pt-3 mbr-light mb=
r-fonts-style display-2" style=3D"text-align: justify"><font color=3D"#3D87=
CB">3.	Is there any additional verification required after receiving a mess=
age of successful account opening from the bank?</font></p></a>=20
          </div>
<div id=3D"collapse3" class=3D"collapse" role=3D"tabpanel" aria-labelledby=
=3D"heading3" data-parent=3D"#accordion1">
	        <div class=3D"card-body">
			=09
				<p style=3D"text-align: justify"><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
				=09
					Yes, the customer is required to conduct biometric verification within=
 60 days of account opening. Bio-metric verification can be done at any bra=
nchless banking agent of your bank.</font></p><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"=
+1">
				<p> </p>
            </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
          </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
        </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
	=09
		<div class=3D"card">
