se" aria-controls=3D"collapse4">
	        <p class=3D"mbr-text mb-3 pt-3 mbr-light mbr-fonts-style display-2=
" style=3D"text-align: justify"><font color=3D"#3D87CB">4.		What will happe=
n if biometric verification is not conducted within 60 days? </font></p></a=
>
          </div>
<div id=3D"collapse4" class=3D"collapse" role=3D"tabpanel" aria-labelledby=
=3D"heading4" data-parent=3D"#accordion1">
	        <div class=3D"card-body">
			=09
				<p style=3D"text-align: justify"><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">The a=
ccount will be debit-blocked after 60 days if no biometric verification is =
conducted.  The customer may visit his /her bank=E2=80=99s nearest branchle=
ss banking agent or bank branch for biometric verification.</font></p><font=
 color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
            </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
          </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
        </font></div><font color=3D"#000" size=3D"+1">
	=09
